Hi , I'm Ignacio Tosini



I am a passionate developer with expertise in front-end technologies like HTML, CSS, SCSS, and JavaScript. I enjoy creating beautiful and functional websites and applications. My goal is to continually improve my skills and contribute to exciting projects that make an impact. Recently, I have been focusing on improving my skills in React. React's component-based architecture has allowed me to create reusable and maintainable code, enhancing both development efficiency and application performance.
